author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Hangzhou Tigermed Consulting revises Q1 2018 net profit outlook
text:
April 9(Reuters) - Hangzhou Tigermed Consulting Co Ltd
* Sees net profit for Q1 2018 to increase by 110 percent to 130 percent, or to be 91.1 million yuan to 99.8 million yuan, compared to net profit of Q1 2017 (43.4 million yuan)
* In the previous outlook, the company expected the net profit for Q1 2018 to increase by 185 percent to 200 percent, or to be 123.6 million yuan to 130.1 million yuan
